  'Surface material: metal, plastic, paper, glass, textile or packaging all influence the best RFID format.',
  'Read distance and speed: a tap-based access flow needs a different solution from a warehouse portal.',
  'Water, liquid and detergent exposure: especially important for laundry, healthcare and hospitality.',
  'Heat, pressure and wear: industrial tags and special materials matter when standard labels will fail.',
  'Reader compatibility: chip family and standard must match the reader already in use or planned for deployment.',
];

const selectionSteps = [
  'Define the application first: access control, asset tracking, product authentication, events, logistics or something else.',
  'Confirm your reader or chip requirement so protocol compatibility is solved before design and printing decisions.',
  'Choose the product format that fits the user flow and operating environment, not just the lowest-cost option.',
  'Test samples in the real environment whenever metal, liquid, custom encoding or special read positions are involved.',
  'Only then lock in artwork, numbering, packaging and production quantities.',
];

const relatedGuides = [
  { href: '/rfid-frequency-guide', label: 'RFID frequency pillar (LF / HF / UHF)', description: 'Companion pillar guide \u2014 decision framework, regional compliance map and cost benchmarks focused only on the frequency choice.' },
  { href: '/rfid-chip-comparison', label: 'RFID chip comparison pillar (MIFARE / NTAG / UCODE)', description: 'Companion pillar guide \u2014 security tier matrix, cost curves, migration paths and counterfeit risk for every major chip family.' },
  { href: '/rfid-vs-nfc-vs-bluetooth', label: 'RFID vs NFC vs Bluetooth pillar', description: 'The first-decision pillar \u2014 when to pick RFID at all vs NFC-only vs BLE vs QR, with hybrid architectures.' },
  { href: '/blogs/rfid-frequency-guide', label: 'RFID frequency tactical deep-dive', description: 'The cluster companion to this pillar, with chip-level LF/HF/UHF and regional specifics.' },
  { href: '/blogs/nfc-technology', label: 'NFC technology guide', description: 'Useful when smartphone tap, marketing or mobile-friendly workflows are part of the project.' },
  { href: '/blogs/rfid-vs-barcode', label: 'RFID vs barcode', description: 'Helpful when an operations team is planning an upgrade from manual scanning.' },
