              Indicative single-unit pricing at MOQ 10,000+ pieces, in USD. Custom artwork, encoding, secure chips and on-metal tuning push prices toward the upper end of each range. Below MOQ 1,000 expect 30-60% premiums; above MOQ 100,000 expect 15-25% discounts.
