            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4 italic">Sources: IDTechEx 2024 RAIN RFID Forecasts; RFIDAK 2026 published price book at MOQ 10,000. Cryptographic chips (NTAG424 DNA, MIFARE DESFire EV3) carry $0.40-1.20 chip premium not reflected in baseline format pricing.</p>
            <div class="mt-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
